node.text: Two Acura pro drivers. Neither had driven the other’s class of #IMSA race car. See what happens during Acura Driver’s Swap. @rickytaylorrace @trenthindman @team_penske @meyershankracing @heinricherracing

Born in Virginia and raised in El Salvador, Ronaldo Ramirez’s #TunedByCultura story started when he moved back to the States and, in car modding, found an outlet to express his identity. 

@tl_ronaldo’s father had a big influence on him, encouraging him to follow his dreams and never give up. Driven by fire and determination, Ronaldo vowed to build something that represents both him and his culture. Thus was born his modded #AcuraTL. “The blue wheels represent El Salvador. My heritage holds special meaning to me.” Ronaldo’s favorite way to celebrate #HispanicHeritageMonth is by driving his Salvadoran-inspired TL on the streets of Atlanta.
